Package hu.bme.mit.theta.sts.dsl.gen

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StsDslListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by StsDslParser.
    StsDslVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by StsDslParser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    StsDslBaseListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of StsDslListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
    StsDslBaseVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of StsDslVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
